data.description: Welcome home to this recently remodeled ranch on just under 1 acre in Senoia! This adorable home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with updates throughout. The open living room features vaulted ceilings and porcelain flooring. The dining room leads to the galley kitchen which has beautiful countertops, white cabinets & stainless steel appliances. Continuing through the kitchen is the pantry and the laundry area. All bedrooms are carpeted and have good sized closets. The fenced backyard features an above ground pool, hot tub and a 16' x 12' outbuilding that is heated and air conditioned. Washer/dryer and kitchen appliances to remain, HVAC is only 2 years old. Add this to your must see list!
